{
  "stem": "23942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to go under into a bunker that night, and the bombs kept falling and falling.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every bomb, I can still remember in my head today.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can still remember how it sounded, even though it was 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole night, the bombs were so close that I thought they were on my head.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because every bomb that came, I can still hear the sound and the noise and I thought that was the last one that was going to hit us, and we will never make it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were sitting crouched, the nuns with the children underneath.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know if it was underneath the church, or I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was in a bunker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now the bunker-- in front of the bunker, in the-- in the garden, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the garden part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were-- the Germans had-- had-- not just machine guns, but they had like-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they had-- they were shooting back against the Russians, because the Russians were-- were throwing down the bomb to win Poland back.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the Germans were not giving up, so they had these big cannon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Cannon.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A small cannon.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were cannons standing right in the garden, and the cannon kept shooting up, and that's why there were-- because the cannons kept going as the planes were going through.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were trying to win the-- the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The cannons were shooting up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so that's why they knew how to find this-- and the bombs were so-- that every bomb that fell the whole night, I thought, that was the last time I'm going to be alive.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a terrible, scary night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And when the morning came, suddenly there was quiet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's when we knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
